name: Unidentified Alien Game
description:
Unidentified Alien Game
Avoid The Obstacles. Reach The End.
The Aliens need to get home.  You have to avoid all the obstacles to reach the end of every level, and try to get the aliens to their home planet.
Inspired by Geometry Dash and Flappy Bird, UAG is a rage game where you have to fly through the obstacles.

HOW TO PLAY
Use the Space Bar to move the player up and down to get through the obstacles.
